00:36:58,840 --> 00:37:01,000
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't say anything wrong.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

517
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:04,840
<font color="#ffffff">You know how much Dao's fiancé hates us.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

518
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:10,120
<font color="#ffffff">You should leave.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Don't bring any more trouble to us.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

519
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:13,760
<font color="#ffffff">I don't want him causing a scene</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">at my brother's funeral.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

520
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,480
<font color="#ffffff">Don't worry.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

521
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,400
<font color="#ffffff">I'm saying goodbye to Dam.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

522
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:18,760
<font color="#ffffff">I'll leave right after.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

523
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:21,320
<font color="#ffffff">I haven't given you permission yet.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

524
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:23,640
<font color="#ffffff">-How can you just walk in?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Sai Kaew!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

525
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:24,840
<font color="#ffffff">Drop the attitude.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

526
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:27,320
<font color="#ffffff">Petch, nobody invited her in.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

527
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:29,160
<font color="#ffffff">I did.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

528
00:37:29,240 --> 00:37:31,360
<font color="#ffffff">You always defend her.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

529
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:34,200
<font color="#ffffff">Do you ever care about my feelings?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

530
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:38,560
<font color="#ffffff">This is Dam's funeral.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

531
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:41,200
<font color="#ffffff">If you care about him,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

532
00:37:42,120 --> 00:37:45,000
<font color="#ffffff">you should act like</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">a better host than this.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

533
00:37:56,360 --> 00:38:00,640
<font color="#ffffff">My brother is barely gone,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and Petch has already changed.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

534
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:05,160
<font color="#ffffff">This is completely absurd.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

535
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:12,000
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know what brought us together,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

536
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:16,680
<font color="#ffffff">and I don't know why</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">you had to leave so soon.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

537
00:38:17,800 --> 00:38:21,480
<font color="#ffffff">But what I know is that</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">we will be friends forever.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

538
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:25,080
<font color="#ffffff">Rest in peace, Damrong.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

539
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:28,640
<font color="#ffffff">DAMRONG LOMONGKOL</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">2000-2023<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

540
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:40,960
<font color="#ffffff">If we hadn't fought yesterday,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

541
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:44,560
<font color="#ffffff">he would still be here today.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

542
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:52,440
<font color="#ffffff">Don't blame yourself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

543
00:38:54,440 --> 00:38:55,840
<font color="#ffffff">I really feel that way.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

544
00:38:57,600 --> 00:38:59,080
<font color="#ffffff">If he weren't my friend,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

545
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,800
<font color="#ffffff">he wouldn't have died like this.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

546
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:07,280
<font color="#ffffff">No one can control life or death.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

547
00:39:08,560 --> 00:39:12,240
<font color="#ffffff">Instead of blaming yourself like this,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

548
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:16,280
<font color="#ffffff">you should honor his last wish.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

549
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:18,840
<font color="#ffffff">That way, his death won't be in vain.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

550
00:39:23,720 --> 00:39:25,160
<font color="#ffffff">Life is short.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

551
00:39:27,240 --> 00:39:28,960
<font color="#ffffff">Hurry back home to your father.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

552
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:34,520
<font color="#ffffff">I'm leaving now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

553
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:37,080
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you for letting me in.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

554
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:39,360
<font color="#ffffff">I'll walk you out.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

555
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:41,920
<font color="#ffffff">It's fine.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

556
00:39:43,200 --> 00:39:45,120
<font color="#ffffff">You're the host. You should stay here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

557
00:40:03,680 --> 00:40:04,680
<font color="#ffffff">Dao!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

558
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,440
<font color="#ffffff">Hello, sir.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

559
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:13,840
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you at Dam's funeral?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

560
00:40:15,160 --> 00:40:16,960
<font color="#ffffff">I haven't told you yet.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

561
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:19,600
<font color="#ffffff">Who did you get the news from?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

562
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:29,240
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry for not telling you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">that I found Petch.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

563
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,360
<font color="#ffffff">Well…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

564
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,280
<font color="#ffffff">It's…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

565
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:36,640
<font color="#ffffff">He told you…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

566
00:40:39,680 --> 00:40:41,240
<font color="#ffffff">not to tell me, didn't he?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

567
00:40:44,120 --> 00:40:45,000
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

568
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:52,360
<font color="#ffffff">Hold on.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

569
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:54,600
<font color="#ffffff">Where are you going?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

570
00:41:03,160 --> 00:41:04,560
<font color="#ffffff">Since Petch</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

571
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:08,480
<font color="#ffffff">doesn't want to see his father,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

572
00:41:09,560 --> 00:41:12,000
<font color="#ffffff">I'll get out of his sight.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

573
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,840
<font color="#ffffff">It's not like that, sir.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

574
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:18,760
<font color="#ffffff">He cares about you a lot.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

575
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:21,520
<font color="#ffffff">He even went</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to watch over you at the hospital.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

576
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:25,000
<font color="#ffffff">You don't have to make excuses for him.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

577
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:31,160
<font color="#ffffff">If he really cared, he would've faced me</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

578
00:41:32,680 --> 00:41:35,040
<font color="#ffffff">instead of hiding from me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

579
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,800
<font color="#ffffff">Because I'm a useless son!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

580
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:53,440
<font color="#ffffff">All I do is cause trouble</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">for you every day.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

581
00:41:53,520 --> 00:41:55,440
<font color="#ffffff">I've never made you proud.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

582
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:59,400
<font color="#ffffff">I just didn't know</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">how I could face you again.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

583
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:02,920
<font color="#ffffff">Is that all it is?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

584
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:08,280
<font color="#ffffff">You act like I'm not your father.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

585
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:14,240
<font color="#ffffff">Do you know that hurts</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

586
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:18,120
<font color="#ffffff">more than a bullet through my heart?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

587
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,240
<font color="#ffffff">No matter how much…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

588
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:24,240
<font color="#ffffff">you resent or blame me,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

589
00:42:25,600 --> 00:42:26,600
<font color="#ffffff">I accept it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

590
00:42:28,640 --> 00:42:31,000
<font color="#ffffff">But after what happened to Dam last night…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

591
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:35,120
<font color="#ffffff">I realized</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

592
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:39,440
<font color="#ffffff">I shouldn't let pride get between us.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

593
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:45,400
<font color="#ffffff">I've made so many mistakes, Dad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

594
00:42:47,160 --> 00:42:48,040
<font color="#ffffff">But today…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

595
00:42:50,320 --> 00:42:52,880
<font color="#ffffff">please let me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">do the right thing just once.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

596
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:14,320
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry, Dad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

597
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:56,840
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

598
00:43:58,440 --> 00:44:00,160
<font color="#ffffff">Seeing you man up</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

599
00:44:01,320 --> 00:44:03,680
<font color="#ffffff">and face your mistakes</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

600
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:07,360
<font color="#ffffff">makes me so proud.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

601
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:23,920
<font color="#ffffff">Dad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

602
00:44:26,720 --> 00:44:28,240
<font color="#ffffff">You silly boy.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

603
00:44:30,680 --> 00:44:32,000
<font color="#ffffff">Remember this.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

604
00:44:34,160 --> 00:44:35,800
<font color="#ffffff">No matter what you do</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

605
00:44:36,320 --> 00:44:38,040
<font color="#ffffff">or what happens,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

606
00:44:40,360 --> 00:44:41,880
<font color="#ffffff">you are my son.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

607
00:44:44,440 --> 00:44:48,000
<font color="#ffffff">There is never a day</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">that I don't love you,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

608
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:50,360
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

609
00:45:14,360 --> 00:45:18,120
<font color="#ffffff">You know? Petch has signed</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">an artist contract with SP Entertainment.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

610
00:45:18,840 --> 00:45:19,880
<font color="#ffffff">Wow!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

611
00:45:20,720 --> 00:45:23,000
<font color="#ffffff">That's a major label!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

612
00:45:23,840 --> 00:45:25,440
<font color="#ffffff">I'm an artist just like you now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

613
00:45:25,520 --> 00:45:26,720
<font color="#ffffff">No.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

614
00:45:26,800 --> 00:45:28,680
<font color="#ffffff">You've gone much further than me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

615
00:45:28,760 --> 00:45:31,360
<font color="#ffffff">I was just a starving artist.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

616
00:45:32,720 --> 00:45:36,920
<font color="#ffffff">If your mother were still here,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">she would be so happy.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

617
00:45:38,720 --> 00:45:39,760
<font color="#ffffff">Petch!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

618
00:45:40,520 --> 00:45:42,160
<font color="#ffffff">Hurry to the temple's bridge!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

619
00:45:42,240 --> 00:45:43,440
<font color="#ffffff">What's wrong?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

620
00:45:43,520 --> 00:45:45,040
<font color="#ffffff">Dam's sister is going to jump!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

621
00:45:45,120 --> 00:45:46,080
<font color="#ffffff">Sai Kaew?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

622
00:45:46,880 --> 00:45:48,120
<font color="#ffffff">This way!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

623
00:45:52,320 --> 00:45:53,360
<font color="#ffffff">Dam.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

624
00:45:54,240 --> 00:45:56,000
<font color="#ffffff">I have no one left.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

625
00:45:58,240 --> 00:45:59,880
<font color="#ffffff">Sai! Sai Kaew!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

626
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:02,160
<font color="#ffffff">-Sai!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-I'm coming with you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

627
00:46:02,240 --> 00:46:04,080
<font color="#ffffff">Stop it! Don't do this!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

628
00:46:04,160 --> 00:46:05,440
<font color="#ffffff">Stay back!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

629
00:46:06,840 --> 00:46:09,080
<font color="#ffffff">Excuse me! Coming through.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

630
00:46:10,720 --> 00:46:11,760
<font color="#ffffff">Petch!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

631
00:46:11,840 --> 00:46:15,640
<font color="#ffffff">Whether I live or die</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">has nothing to do with you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

632
00:46:15,720 --> 00:46:16,720
<font color="#ffffff">Leave me alone!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

633
00:46:16,800 --> 00:46:20,480
<font color="#ffffff">Did you forget</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">that Dam left you in my care?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

634
00:46:21,520 --> 00:46:26,680
<font color="#ffffff">If Dam hadn't asked,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">you wouldn't care about me.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

635
00:46:28,000 --> 00:46:31,760
<font color="#ffffff">You would just abandon me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to be with the one you love.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

636
00:46:31,840 --> 00:46:33,000
<font color="#ffffff">Nonsense.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

637
00:46:34,360 --> 00:46:35,720
<font color="#ffffff">Stop making things up.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

638
00:46:35,800 --> 00:46:37,360
<font color="#ffffff">You'd better stop talking.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

639
00:46:38,600 --> 00:46:41,880
<font color="#ffffff">I know I'm just an outsider to you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

640
00:46:44,080 --> 00:46:46,560
<font color="#ffffff">Go ahead and be with the one you love.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

641
00:46:48,960 --> 00:46:50,360
<font color="#ffffff">I'm going to be with Dam.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

642
00:46:51,280 --> 00:46:52,160
<font color="#ffffff">Fine.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

643
00:46:53,320 --> 00:46:54,880
<font color="#ffffff">You want to be with him, right?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

644
00:46:54,960 --> 00:46:56,080
<font color="#ffffff">Petch!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

645
00:46:56,160 --> 00:46:58,240
<font color="#ffffff">-Then let's go together, shall we?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Petch!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

646
00:46:58,880 --> 00:47:01,240
<font color="#ffffff">-Jump! So we can die together!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Petch!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

647
00:47:01,320 --> 00:47:04,120
<font color="#ffffff">-Go ahead. Jump!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Have you lost your mind?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

648
00:47:04,200 --> 00:47:06,360
<font color="#ffffff">You wanted to die, didn't you?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Why stop me?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

649
00:47:06,440 --> 00:47:07,920
<font color="#ffffff">No!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

650
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:10,280
<font color="#ffffff">Who would want you to die?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

651
00:47:11,120 --> 00:47:13,400
<font color="#ffffff">Do you know how worried I am about you?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

652
00:47:14,320 --> 00:47:16,080
<font color="#ffffff">Now you know how it feels.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

653
00:47:16,880 --> 00:47:19,800
<font color="#ffffff">If anything happens to you,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I would be just as devastated.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

654
00:47:22,160 --> 00:47:23,920
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

655
00:47:28,040 --> 00:47:29,720
<font color="#ffffff">Come on. Let's go!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

656
00:47:33,440 --> 00:47:34,920
<font color="#ffffff">Step back first.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

657
00:47:39,080 --> 00:47:40,400
<font color="#ffffff">Have a seat, Sai.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

658
00:47:45,560 --> 00:47:46,600
<font color="#ffffff">Sai.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

659
00:47:47,480 --> 00:47:49,000
<font color="#ffffff">We're a family.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

660
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:52,240
<font color="#ffffff">We've already lost Dam.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

661
00:47:53,120 --> 00:47:55,040
<font color="#ffffff">I won't let myself lose you too.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

662
00:47:55,120 --> 00:47:57,240
<font color="#ffffff">Are you serious?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

663
00:47:57,920 --> 00:48:00,160
<font color="#ffffff">Please don't abandon me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

664
00:48:04,520 --> 00:48:06,080
<font color="#ffffff">Even if the world ends,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

665
00:48:07,760 --> 00:48:09,680
<font color="#ffffff">I will never abandon you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

666
00:48:13,600 --> 00:48:14,920
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

667
00:48:19,360 --> 00:48:20,920
<font color="#ffffff">Looks like Dam's sister</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

668
00:48:22,400 --> 00:48:23,960
<font color="#ffffff">is really attached to Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

669
00:48:27,040 --> 00:48:27,920
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

670
00:48:29,440 --> 00:48:32,960
<font color="#ffffff">She loves and looks up to him.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

671
00:48:42,280 --> 00:48:43,280
<font color="#ffffff">Hey!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

672
00:48:43,840 --> 00:48:44,680
<font color="#ffffff">Dao!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

673
00:48:45,200 --> 00:48:46,720
<font color="#ffffff">Where are you going?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

674
00:48:46,800 --> 00:48:47,720
<font color="#ffffff">Dao!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

675
00:49:08,560 --> 00:49:11,960
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Where are you now, honey?</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Ake is waiting for dinner.</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

676
00:49:12,040 --> 00:49:13,040
<font color="#ffffff">I'm on my way back.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

677
00:49:13,920 --> 00:49:17,520
<font color="#ffffff">Great. I've ordered</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">a bunch of new outfits for you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

678
00:49:17,600 --> 00:49:19,440
<font color="#ffffff">They're all my favorite designs.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

679
00:49:19,520 --> 00:49:21,600
<font color="#ffffff">Let's try them when you're back.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

680
00:49:23,080 --> 00:49:24,000
<font color="#ffffff">Sure.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

681
00:49:33,280 --> 00:49:35,400
<font color="#ffffff">Go wash your face first.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

682
00:49:35,480 --> 00:49:36,800
<font color="#ffffff">Okay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

683
00:49:42,720 --> 00:49:44,000
<font color="#ffffff">How is she doing?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

684
00:49:46,920 --> 00:49:48,440
<font color="#ffffff">She has stopped crying.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

685
00:49:53,040 --> 00:49:55,160
<font color="#ffffff">-Where's Dao?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-She just left a moment ago.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

686
00:49:56,280 --> 00:49:58,480
<font color="#ffffff">Please take care of Sai for me.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'll be back.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

687
00:50:07,160 --> 00:50:08,280
<font color="#ffffff">In the past…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

688
00:50:10,720 --> 00:50:12,120
<font color="#ffffff">I've done you so much wrong.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

689
00:50:12,200 --> 00:50:13,360
<font color="#ffffff">Say no more.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

690
00:50:14,840 --> 00:50:16,360
<font color="#ffffff">What are you doing?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

691
00:50:16,440 --> 00:50:18,040
<font color="#ffffff">Let's talk business.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

692
00:50:18,680 --> 00:50:19,520
<font color="#ffffff">What business?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

693
00:50:19,600 --> 00:50:21,400
<font color="#ffffff">I know how much you hate Natedao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

694
00:50:22,240 --> 00:50:23,680
<font color="#ffffff">When she's around Petch…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

695
00:50:24,560 --> 00:50:26,520
<font color="#ffffff">We're on the same page.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

696
00:50:26,600 --> 00:50:27,520
<font color="#ffffff">Let's work together.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

697
00:50:27,600 --> 00:50:30,840
<font color="#ffffff">NEXT EPISODE</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

698
00:50:44,920 --> 00:50:50,000
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if I ever crossed your mind</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

699
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:56,000
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if you heard the whisper</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

700
00:50:56,960 --> 00:51:02,920
<font color="#ffffff"><i>For my heart is crying out my love</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>It's deep and true</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

701
00:51:03,000 --> 00:51:07,760
<font color="#ffffff"><i>But never reaching you</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

702
00:51:09,000 --> 00:51:14,000
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I know that it simply cannot be</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

703
00:51:15,040 --> 00:51:20,080
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to cause you misery</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

704
00:51:21,400 --> 00:51:26,720
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I'm just an ordinary man</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Worth nothing at all</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

705
00:51:27,520 --> 00:51:32,280
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to make</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Your teardrops fall</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

706
00:51:33,840 --> 00:51:38,320
<font color="#ffffff"><i>You are out of reach</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

707
00:51:38,920 --> 00:51:44,000
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Is it a crime that I need you?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

708
00:51:46,040 --> 00:51:50,200
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Please let me know for sure</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

709
00:51:50,800 --> 00:51:56,160
<font color="#ffffff"><i>That you're the one I've been waiting for</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

710
00:51:57,040 --> 00:52:01,480
<font color="#ffffff"><i>How much longer can I bear this pain?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

711
00:52:03,040 --> 00:52:08,000
<font color="#ffffff"><i>How much longer must I wait in vain?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

712
00:52:09,000 --> 00:52:13,960
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I really don't know what move to make</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

713
00:52:15,000 --> 00:52:20,400
<font color="#ffffff"><i>To end this heartache</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And say that I love you</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

714
00:52:20,480 --> 00:52:22,440
<font color="#ffffff">Subtitle translation by: Jarut K.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>
